description: GNC Women's Ultra Mega Energy and Metabolism Clinically Studied Multivitamin^  GNC Women's Ultra Mega Energy and Metabolism has more antioxidant power than ever and over 30 clinically studied ingredients in every formula - all in smaller, easier to swallow pills. Women's Health: Contains a clinically studied women's multivitamin formula shown to work better than a basic multivitamin. Helps to support bone health.* Energy: Shown to improve levels of key B vitamins^ essential for energy production.* Calorie Burning: Features a combination of thermogenic ingredients that may support calorie burning and mental sharpness.* Antioxidants: Packed with antioxidants to help fight free radicals that can be produced by intense exercise.* ^In a randomized, double-blinded placebo-controlled study of 112 healthy volunteers, subjects taking GNC vitamin and mineral blends for six weeks experienced significant improvements in serum levels of certain key nutrients compared to a placebo and a leading multivitamin formula based upon multivariate statistical analysis of a group of B vitamins (thiamin, niacin, riboflavin, pantothenic acid, biotin, folic acid and vitamins B-6 and B-12) and key antioxidants and carotenoids (a group of beta-carotene, alpha-tocopherol, selenium, lutein and lycopene). Statistical improvements in SF-36 Vitality and Mental Health scores were also observed compared to placebo.
